headline: GPC Q2 Deep Dive: Tariffs, Cost Actions, and Cautious Outlook Shape Results
summary: Auto and industrial parts retailer Genuine Parts (NYSE:GPC) reported Q2 CY2025 results exceeding the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 3.4% year on year to $6.16 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.10 per share was 2.1% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
